const actions = {
    addMoment: (store, moments, newMoment) => {
        console.log(store)
        console.log(moments)
        console.log(newMoment)
        var newMoments = moments.slice(0).
        newMoments.push(newMoment)
        console.log("Printing store and new moments")
        console.log(newMoments)
        console.log("This is newMoments: " + newMoments)
        store.setState({moments: newMoments})
    }
}

export default actions
